292
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,560
There are so many docks in the west.

293
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:34,760
How will you find her?

294
00:14:36,400 --> 00:14:38,320
Jiangcheng has seven docks in total.

295
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:41,720
Two of them are large commercial ports with strict surveillance.

296
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,720
The other five are old fishing ports

297
00:14:46,680 --> 00:14:48,280
and private yacht marinas.

298
00:14:49,520 --> 00:14:51,720
Their management is relatively loose.

299
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:57,320
Zhai,

300
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:01,280
have the technicians cross-reference two sets of data.

301
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:02,010
The first set

302
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:04,210
is from the 'Listen to Her' app,

303
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:05,520
including all professions

304
00:15:05,520 --> 00:15:07,800
related to boats, fishery, shipping,

305
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,000
and dock management.

306
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:10,520
The second set

307
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,560
is within 24 hours,

308
00:15:13,560 --> 00:15:14,480
all

309
00:15:14,800 --> 00:15:15,730
personal yachts

310
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,960
and private docks

311
00:15:17,280 --> 00:15:18,560
that have abnormal reports

312
00:15:18,560 --> 00:15:19,960
and unusual activities.

313
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:20,640
Right.

314
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:22,050
Just these two sets.

315
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:23,440
Got it.

316
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:26,320
Chen, there is one match.

317
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,960
A fishing boat owner named Li Hong

318
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,560
was once a user of 'Listen to Her'.

319
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:31,440
The port surveillance in the West Port District shows

320
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:33,640
that after her cargo ship finished unloading this evening,

321
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:35,600
it didn't return to the port for fixed docking as usual.

322
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:37,040
Instead, it abnormally moved to

323
00:15:37,040 --> 00:15:39,840
the abandoned Berth 7, a surveillance blind spot.

324
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,180
I'm going then.

325
00:15:44,640 --> 00:15:45,440
Safety first.

326
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:49,040
You stay safe too.

327
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:52,620
Protect yourself.

328
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:55,800
Aunt Rong!

329
00:15:56,800 --> 00:15:57,400
Don't run!

330
00:15:58,920 --> 00:16:00,520
Turn back before it's too late!

331
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:01,050
Qiu Chen!

332
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:03,400
I have ALS.

333
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:04,930
I don't have much time left.

334
00:16:05,880 --> 00:16:08,120
I just want to find a quiet place to die.

335
00:16:08,120 --> 00:16:09,250
Can't I even do that?

336
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:11,520
Why are you still lying to me?

337
00:16:12,480 --> 00:16:12,920
First,

338
00:16:14,600 --> 00:16:15,880
you don't have ALS.

339
00:16:16,560 --> 00:16:19,490
You forged all those medical records and diagnoses.

340
00:16:19,680 --> 00:16:20,140
Second,

341
00:16:20,800 --> 00:16:22,600
you aren't going to die quietly.

342
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:26,050
You want to go abroad to continue your cleaner business.

343
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:29,020
You've already obtained foreign citizenship.

344
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:31,040
Once you escape to the high seas,

345
00:16:31,680 --> 00:16:33,940
it will be much harder for us to catch you.

346
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:35,400
I can tell you

347
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:37,680
that all the ports right now

348
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:39,680
have been locked down by the police.

349
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,080
You can't escape.

350
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:42,080
Is that so?

351
00:16:43,800 --> 00:16:45,560
Then if I take you as a hostage,

352
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:48,480
I can force them to clear a path, right?
